item.description:
Leaflet-providers An extension to Leaflet that contains configurations for various free1 tile providers.
Usage Leaflet-providers providers are refered to with a provider[.&lt;variant&gt;]-string. Let&rsquo;s say you want to add the nice Watercolor style from Stamen to your map, you pass Stamen.Watercolor to the L.tileLayer.provider-constructor, which will return a L.TileLayer instance for Stamens Watercolor tile layer.
// add Stamen Watercolor to map. L.tileLayer.provider('Stamen.Watercolor').addTo(map);  Protocol relativity (https://-urls) Leaflet-providers tries to use https:// if the page uses https:// and the provider supports it.
